Smart AI assistant
==================

Aaron is a smart IOT based home assistant which can be controlled using voice commands and let you to control your home appliances.

It can learn new skills and can be programmed to perform actions.

It is still under development and i will be adding AI to Aaron ( Currently you have to create the skill )

Hardware
--------

I used Raspberry PI and created a relay circuit in order to control the eletrical appliances.

Other
-----

Created a Facebook Bot too, which was connected to the backend service of the aaron-iot and 
could be used to control electrical appliances.
